messages.speech:
You don't need to check the Corona Virus
There are many common viruses other than corona that cause 
your symptoms. Based on your answers, you do not need to 
check the virus at this time.
We hope that anyone who develops symptoms that include coughing, runny nose, fever and sore throat will self-quit for 14 days.
To protect yourself in public places, please wash your hands frequently and intensively, and keep at least 2 meters from the surroundings.
If the symptoms worsen or if you are interested in learning more, contact the nursing staff in your country.
How else may I help?
